properties.Description: The properties of the create webhook operation.

isEnabled.Description: Gets or sets the value of the enabled flag of webhook.

expiryTime.Description: Gets or sets the expiry time.

parameters.Description: Gets or sets the parameters of the job.

runbook.Description: The runbook property associated with the entity.

runOn.Description: Gets or sets the name of the hybrid worker group the webhook job will run on.

lastInvokedTime.Description: Gets or sets the last invoked time.

creationTime.Description: Gets or sets the creation time.

lastModifiedTime.Description: Gets or sets the last modified time.

lastModifiedBy.Description: Details of the user who last modified the Webhook

name.Description: Gets or sets the name of the runbook.
